519
00:50:48,366 --> 00:50:50,771
Not everything.

520
00:50:53,159 --> 00:50:54,776
Francois was there.

521
00:50:54,777 --> 00:50:58,383
He is a killer. He is one of them.

522
00:51:01,349 --> 00:51:03,530
Did you see him kill anyone?

523
00:51:03,531 --> 00:51:09,920
